Mutane da yawa sun makale a cikin baragunan gine-gine da suka rushe a lokacin girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 da ta afku a ranar Juma'a, wanda ya haifar da raƙuman ruwa masu tsawon mita 6, kamar yadda mai magana da yawun hukumar Sutopo Purwo Nugroho ya bayyana a wani taron manema labarai.
Birnin Palu, mai mutane fiye da 380,000, yana cike da tarkacen gine-gine da suka rushe.
