Hukumar Kula da Yanayi ta Amurka ta ba da gargadin ambaliyar ruwa a ranar Litinin da Talata daga yammacin Arizona zuwa kudu da gabashin Nevada, kudu maso gabashin California da Utah, ciki har da Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas da Salt Lake City.
