A cewar U.S. Drought Monitor, fiye da kashi 40 na Arizona suna fuskantar akalla matsanancin fari, na biyu mafi girma, weather.com ta ruwaito.
Na farko, Hurricane Rosa zai kai gabas a yankin Baja California na Mexico.
