Sau biyu ne kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup inda wata kungiya ta samu maki hudu a wasan mutum, duk da cewa a matsayin mai riƙe da kofin yanzu, tawagar Furyk ta bukaci a daidaita su don kiyaye shi.
Duk da haka, bayan kasancewa na biyu mafi kyau a cikin kwana biyu, wani hari a ranar Lahadi kamar ba zai yiwu ba.
Arewacin Koriya ta ce babu wani shirin kashe makamai idan babu amincewa
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa takunkumin na kara sabawa Amurka, kuma kasar ba za ta mika makaman nukiliyarta ba a irin wannan yanayi.
Ri Yong Ho ya sanar da babban taron shekara-shekara cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki "matakai masu muhimmanci don nuna kyakkyawar niyyarta" a shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da makaman nukiliya, da lalata filayen gwajin nukiliya da kuma sadaukar da kai ga yaduwar makaman nukiliya da fasaha.
"Duk da haka, ba mu ga irin wannan martani daga Amurka ba", in ji shi.
"Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba, ba za a iya amincewa da tsaron kasa ba, kuma a irin wannan yanayi, ba za a iya samun kawar da makamai ba da farko daga gare mu".
Yayin da Ri ya sake maimaita korafe-korafen da aka saba yi a Koriya ta Arewa game da kin amincewa da Washington kan kawar da makaman nukiliya "a hankali" wanda a karkashinsa za a ba Koriya ta Arewa lada yayin da take daukar matakai, sanarwar tasa ta yi kama da muhimmiyar magana, saboda ba ta ki amincewa da kawar da makaman nukiliya ta bangare daya ba kamar yadda ya faru da Pyongyang a baya.
Ri ya yi nuni da wata sanarwa ta hadin gwiwa da Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump suka yi a taron farko tsakanin shugaban Amurka mai ci da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa da aka gudanar a Singapore a ranar 12 ga watan Yuni, lokacin da Kim ya yi alkawarin "kawar da makaman nukiliya" daga yankin Koriya ta Kudu yayin da Trump ya tabbatar da tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa ta dade tana neman kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta fara ajiye makaman nukiliya.
Har ila yau, Washington ta yi tawaye wajen sassauta takunkumin kasa da kasa kan Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ta dage kan 'kafarar makaman nukiliya da farko' kuma tana kara matsa lamba ta hanyar takunkumi don cimma burinta na yin takunkumi, kuma duk da cewa tana adawa da 'yancin yakin,'" in ji Ri.
"Ganin cewa takunkumi zai iya sa mu durƙusa mafarki ne da ba zai yiwu ba ga wanda bai san mu ba.
Amma matsalar ita ce, takunkumi na ci gaba da kara sa mu cikin rashin amincewa.
Ri bai ambaci shirin taron Kim da Trump na biyu ba, wanda shugaban Amurka ya ambata a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon.
Sai dai ya yi magana game da tarurruka uku tsakanin Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata, ya kuma kara da cewa: "Idan bangaren wannan batun na kawar da makaman nukiliya ya kasance Koriya ta Kudu ba Amurka ba, to kawar da makaman nukiliya daga yankin Koriya ba zai kai ga matsi ba".
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Ri ya sha bambam da na shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da ya fadawa babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa ba makawa ne a kai hari kan Amurka da makamai masu linzami na Koriya ta Arewa bayan da "mummunan" shugaban kasa Trump ya kira Kim "mutumin roka" a wani aikin kisan kai.
A wannan shekara a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Trump, wanda bara ya yi barazanar "hallaka Koriya ta Arewa gaba daya", ya yaba wa Kim saboda jarumtarsa wajen daukar matakan kawar da makamai, amma ya ce har yanzu akwai aiki da yawa da za a yi, kuma dole ne a ci gaba da takunkumi har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta kawar da makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce babu lokacin da za a yi wannan, kuma duk abin da zai ɗauki shekaru biyu, uku ko biyar".
Sin da Rasha na tattaunawa kan ko ya kamata kwamitin sulhu na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya saka wa Pyongyang bisa matakan da ta dauka.
Amma a ranar Alhamis, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya shaida wa Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa: "Ya kamata a ci gaba da aiwatar da takunkumin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya da karfi ba tare da wani banda ba har sai mun ga cikakkiyar, karshe da kuma tabbatar da kawar da makaman nukiliya".
Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya amince da tsauraran takunkumi kan Koriya ta Arewa tun 2006 a wani yunkuri na yanke kudade ga shirin nukiliya da makamin nukiliya na Pyongyang.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a gefen taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya sannan ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe domin shirya taron kolin na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekara, amma tafiyarsa ta karshe ba ta yi kyau ba.
Ya bar birnin Pyongyang a watan Yuli yana mai cewa ya samu ci gaba, sa'o'i kadan bayan da Koriya ta Arewa ta zarge shi da yin "bunkasa da ta shafi 'yan ta'adda".
A wani taro da Moon ya yi a wannan watan, Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin rushe wani wurin da ake da makaman nukiliya da kuma wani wurin da ake da makaman nukiliya idan Amurka ta dauki matakan da suka dace.
Ya ce Kim ya gaya masa cewa "matakan da suka dace" da ya nema su ne tabbacin tsaro da Trump ya yi alkawari a Singapore da kuma ci gaba zuwa daidaita dangantakar da Washington.
Dalibai a Harvard suna gudanar da wani darasi game da samun isasshen hutu
A wannan shekara, wani sabon darasi a Jami'ar Harvard yana sa dukan ɗalibansa su yi barci sosai domin yaƙi da al'adar jima'i na yin karatu dare da rana da ke cike da maganin kafeyin.
Wani manazarci ya gano cewa ɗalibai a jami'a mafi girma a duniya sau da yawa ba su san ainihin yadda za su kula da kansu ba.
Charles Czeisler, farfesa a fannin maganin bacci a Harvard Medical School kuma kwararre a asibitin Brigham da Muller, ya tsara wannan darasi, wanda ya yi imanin shi ne na farko a Amurka.
Ta samu kwarin gwiwa ta fara wannan darasi ne bayan da ta gabatar da wani jawabi game da tasirin rashin bacci a kan ilmantarwa.
"A ƙarshen karatun, wata yarinya ta zo wurina, ta ce, 'Me ya sa ba a gaya mini wannan ba sai yanzu, a shekarar karshe?'
Ya ce ba a taɓa gaya masa muhimmancin barci ba, abin da ya ba ni mamaki", in ji shi a The Telegraph.
Wannan darasi, wanda aka fara shi a wannan shekara, ya koya wa ɗalibai game da yadda samun halayen barci mai kyau ke taimakawa ga aikin ilimi da na wasanni, da kuma inganta lafiyar jiki.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar dan adam a makarantar likitanci ta Harvard kuma babban daraktan ayyukan kiwon lafiya na jami'ar, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da wannan darasi ne bayan ta gano cewa dalibai suna da matukar rashin bacci a cikin mako.
Darasi na awa ɗaya yana ɗauke da ayyuka masu ma'ana.
A wani bangare akwai hoton ɗakin kwana, inda ɗalibai suke danna kofuna na kofi, labule, masu koyarwa da littattafai don samun bayani game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske da kuma yadda rashin bacci ke shafar wasan motsa jiki da kuma muhimmancin samun tsarin bacci.
Wani sashe kuma ya gaya wa masu halarta yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci zai iya ƙara haɗarin ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, baƙin ciki, da kuma ciwon daji.
Taswirar harabar da ke dauke da gumaka masu ma'ana tana ƙarfafa masu halarta su yi tunani game da rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum.
"Mun san cewa ba za ka canja halayen ɗalibai nan take ba.
Amma mun yi imanin cewa suna da hakkin su san wannan bayanin, kamar yadda muke da hakkin mu san abin da ke faruwa da lafiyarmu idan muka zaɓi shan taba", in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Ya ce, al'adar yin alfahari da kasancewa a farke har dare har yanzu tana nan, ya kuma kara da cewa, fasaha ta zamani da kuma karuwar matsin lamba ga dalibai wanda ya hada da rashin bacci, ya kasance wata matsala mai karuwa.
Ya ce, tabbatar da cewa dalibi yana samun isasshen barci da kuma ingancinsa ya kamata ya zama "makaminsa na sirri" wajen yaki da damuwa, gajiya da kuma damuwa, har ma da guje wa kiba, domin rashin barci yana sa kwakwalwa ta shiga yanayin yunwa, wanda ke sa mutum ya ci gaba da jin yunwa.
Raymond So, dan California mai shekara 19 da ke nazarin kimiyyar lissafi da ilimin halittu, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Czeisler wajen tsara wannan darasi, bayan ya halarci ɗaya daga cikin darussansa a shekarar da ta gabata a shekara ta farko a Harvard.
Ya ce wannan darasi ya sa ya yi farin ciki kuma ya sa ya soma koyar da darasi a dukan makarantar.
Mataki na gaba, da fatan, shine a nemi dukkan daliban digiri su kammala irin wannan shirin kafin su shiga makarantar.
Farfesa Czeisler ya shawarci ɗalibai su yi la'akari da kafa ƙararrawa don lokacin barci da lokacin farkawa. Hakazalika, ana ba da shawarar cewa su san da illa na "hasken shuɗi" da ke fitowa daga allon lantarki da hasken LED, wanda zai iya daidaita yanayin circadian kuma ya haifar da matsalolin bacci.
Livingston 1-0 Rangers: Kwallon Menga ya ci mutanen Gerrard
Rangers sun sha wahala wani mummunan labari lokacin da harin Dolly Menga ya jefa Steven Gerrard's team a cikin rashin nasara 1-0 a Livingston.
Kungiyar Ibrox ta yi niyyar cin nasarar farko a gida tun bayan nasarar 4-1 a St Johnstone a watan Fabrairu, amma Gary Holt ya sa Gerrard ya ci karo na biyu a wasanni 18 a matsayin kocin, wanda ya bar kungiyar ta maki takwas daga Hearts, shugabannin kungiyar Ladbrokes Premiership, Scottish League.
Menga ya kai hari minti bakwai kafin hutu kuma Rangers din da ke da karamin kwarin gwiwa bai taba jin kamar zai ci karo ba.
Yayin da Rangers suka sauka zuwa matsayi na shida, Livingston ya hau zuwa matsayi na uku kuma yana bin Hibernian ne kawai da ci daya.
Kuma zai iya zama mafi muni ga Rangers bayan da alkalin wasa Calum Spence ya yi fama da rauni a kai bayan da aka yi masa zargin jefa wani abu.
Gerrard ya yi sau takwas daga tawagar da ta doke Ayr a wasan kusa da na karshe na gasar cin kofin Betfred, ko gasar cin kofin zakarun Scotland.
A gefe guda kuma, Holt ya yi daidai da 11 na Livingston wanda ya ci Hearts kwallo a makon da ya gabata kuma zai yi farin ciki da yadda kungiyarsa ta yi ta murkushe abokan hamayyarsu a kowane lokaci.
Rangers sun iya mamaye mallaka, amma Livingston ya yi fiye da haka lokacin da suke da kwallon.
Da sun iya zira kwallaye cikin minti biyu lokacin da aka buga wasan farko na Menga wanda ya tura Scott Pittman zuwa ƙofar Allan McGregor, amma dan wasan ya ɓata wannan babbar dama.
Wani babban harbi na Keaghan Jacobs ya kai ga Kyaftin Craig Halkett, amma abokin aikinsa na kare Alan Lithgow, ya sami damar buga shi a ƙwallon ƙafa na biyu.
Rangers sun dauki ragamar, amma sun fi fatan samun nasara a wasan da suke yi a filin wasa.
Babu shakka, Alfredo Morelos ya ji cewa ya kamata su buga kwallo a minti na 15 lokacin da shi da Steven Lawless suka yi karo, amma alkalin wasa, Steven Thomson, ya yi watsi da ikirarin dan wasan Colombia.
Rangers sun buga kwallo biyu a raga a farkon rabin, amma tsohon dan wasan Ibrox, Liam Kelly, ya sha wahala ne kawai a kan ciwon kai na Lassana Coulibaly da kuma harin Ovie Ejaria.
Yayin da Livingston ya bude a minti na 34 zai iya zama ya sabawa ka'idar wasan, babu wanda zai iya musanta cewa sun cancanci hakan saboda aiki tuƙuru da suka yi.
Rangers sun sake kasawa yayin da suka fuskanci Jacobs mai karfi.
Scott Arfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya sanya kwallon zuwa Scott Robinson, wanda ya ci gaba da jin dadi don ya zabi Menga don daya daga cikin matakai.
Gerrard ya yi aiki a lokacin hutu ta hanyar canza Coulibaly zuwa Ryan Kent, canji wanda ya kusan tasiri nan da nan lokacin da hagu ya ba da izinin Morelos, amma mai girma Kelly ya gudu daga layinsa don toshe shi.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da cinye baƙi ta hanyar wasa daidai irin wasan da suke so, tare da Lithgow da Halkett suna ɗaukar dogon ball bayan wani.
Holt's team zai iya fadada fifiko a cikin minti na ƙarshe, amma McGregor ya tashi daidai don ya ƙi Jacobs kafin Lithgow ya hau daga kusurwa.
Mai maye gurbin Rangers, Glenn Middleton, ya sake neman fansa yayin da ya shiga cikin Jacobs, amma Thomson ya sake yin watsi da shi.
Almanac: wanda ya kirkiro Geiger counter
Kuma yanzu shafi na mu na "Sunday Morning": 30 ga Satumba, 1882, shekaru 136 da suka wuce, a yau, kuma an ƙidaya... shi ne ranar da aka haifi masanin kimiyyar lissafi Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya kirkiro wata hanya ta ganowa da auna radiyo, wani kirkire-kirkire da ya kai shi ga na'urar da ake kira Geiger counter.
Wani ginshiƙi na kimiyya tun daga wannan lokacin, Geiger counter ya zama babban ɓangare na al'adun gargajiya, kamar a cikin fim din 1950 "Bells of Coronado" (Bells of Coronado), wanda ya ƙunshi waɗannan masana kimiyya masu ban mamaki Roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Mutum: "Mece ce wannan a duniya?"
Rogers: "Wannan na'urar Geiger ce, da ake amfani da ita wajen gano ma'adanai masu aikin rediyo, kamar su Uranium.
Idan ka saka waɗannan belun kunne, za ka iya jin tasirin da atom ke yi daga rediyo da ke fitowa daga ma'adanai".
Evans: "Ya ce, "Na tabbata yana fashewa yanzu!"
"Hans" Geiger ya mutu a 1945, 'yan kwanaki bayan ranar haihuwarsa ta 63.
Amma abin da ya yi ya rayu.
Sabuwar rigakafin cutar kansa na iya koyar da tsarin garkuwar jikinka ta "ga" ƙwayoyin cuta da suka lalace
Sabuwar rigakafin cutar kansa na iya koyar da tsarin garkuwar jikinka ta "ga" ƙwayoyin cuta da suka lalace
Rigakafin yana koya wa tsarin garkuwar jikin mutum gane kwayoyin cuta da suka lalace a matsayin wani bangare na magani.
Wannan hanya ta ƙunshi cire ƙwayoyin cuta daga cikin marasa lafiya, kuma a canja su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje.
Za ka iya ganin furotin da ke da amfani ga wasu nau'o'in ciwon daji, kuma ka sake yin allurar.
Wani rigakafin gwaji yana nuna kyakkyawan sakamako a cikin marasa lafiya da ke da ciwon daji iri-iri.
Wata mata da aka yi mata allurar rigakafi, wadda take koya wa tsarin garkuwar jikinta gane ƙwayoyin cuta da ba su da kyau, ta ga ciwon daji na cikin mahaifarta ya ɓace na tsawon watanni 18.
Wannan hanyar tana ɗaukan ƙwayoyin cuta daga wani mai ciwon daji, kuma a yi musu gyara a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje don su iya "ganin" wani furotin da ke da amfani a yawancin ciwon daji da ake kira HER2, kuma su ƙi ƙwayoyin.
Farfesa Jay Berzofsky, na Cibiyar Kula da Ciwon daji ta Amurka a Bethesda, Maryland, ya ce: "Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa muna da rigakafin da ke da matukar alƙawarin".
HER2 tana "ƙarfafa ciwon daji iri-iri", har da na nono, na mahaifa, na huhu, da kuma na farji, in ji Farfesa Berzofsky.
Irin wannan tsarin da ake amfani da shi wajen cire ƙwayoyin cuta daga marasa lafiya da kuma koya musu su kai hari ga ƙwayoyin cutar kansa ya yi aiki wajen magance wani nau'in cutar sankarar bargo.
Kanye West ya shiga cikin jawabin goyon bayan Trump ta hanyar sanya MAGA (Make America Great Again) hat bayan fitowar sa a shirin Saturday Night Live (SNL).
Kuma sakamakon bai kasance mai kyau ba.
A wani shirin na Saturday Night Live, Kanye West ya shiga cikin studio bayan wani gabatarwa mai rikitarwa inda ya yaba wa shugaban Amurka, Donald Trump, kuma ya ce zai tsaya takara a 2020.
Bayan da ta yi waka ta uku a daren, mai suna "Ghost Town", inda ta saka hular Make America Great Again, ta soki 'yan Democrat kuma ta sake jaddada goyon bayanta ga Trump.
"Ina yawan magana da fararen fata, sai na ce, "Ta yaya za ka so Trump idan shi dan wariyar launin fata ne?"
Idan na damu da wariyar launin fata, da na bar Amurka tun da daɗewa", in ji shi.
SNL ta fara shirin ne da wani satire mai suna Matt Damon, wanda a ciki tauraron Hollywood din ya yi wa shaidar Brett Kavanaugh ba'a a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya game da kararrakin cin zarafin jima'i da Christine Blasey Ford ta yi.
Ko da yake ba a watsa shi ba, Chris Rock ya ɗora hotunan da suka yi wa West suka yi a shafukan sada zumunta.
Ba a bayyana ba ko Rock yana ƙoƙarin yin ba'a ga West tare da wannan post ɗin.
Bugu da ƙari, West ya yi gunaguni ga masu sauraro cewa ya yi mummunan lokaci a baya bayan fage saboda hatinsa.
"An yi mini ba'a a bayan fage.
Suka ce, 'Kada ka fita da wannan hat.'
Sun tsoratar da ni!
Sai suka ce na yi hauka", in ji shi a Washington Examiner.
West ya ci gaba da cewa, "Kuna son ganin yadda zan yi wasa?" yana cewa zan "yi amfani da kwalkwali na superman, domin yana nufin ba za ku iya gaya mani abin da zan yi ba.
Ka yi ƙoƙari ka ƙaunace shi".
Maganganunsa sun haifar da ƙyamar sauraro a kalla sau biyu kuma membobin ƙungiyar SNL sun bayyana sun kunyata, ya ba da rahoto ga mujallar Variety, tare da wannan shaidar da wani mutum da ke wurin ya ba da gabatarwa: "Dukkanin binciken ya kasance cikin shiru".
An nada West a matsayin sabon maye gurbin Ariana Grande, wacce tsohon saurayinta, dan wasan rap din Mac Miller, ya mutu kwanakin baya.
West ya ba mutane da yawa mamaki tare da yin waƙa da aka yi da "Ina son shi", wanda aka yi ado kamar kwalban ruwa na Perrier.
West ta samu goyon bayan shugaban kungiyar TPUSA mai ra'ayin mazan jiya, Candace Turner, wacce ta rubuta a shafin Twitter: "Ga daya daga cikin mafiya karfin zuciya: Godiya ga tsayawa kan Mafia".
Duk da haka, mai gabatar da shirin hira Karen Hunter ta wallafa a shafin Twitter cewa West yana "yin abin da yake, kuma abin ban mamaki ne".
"Saboda haka, na zabi BA zan saka wa kowa ba (ta hanyar sayen kiɗan su ko tufafinsu ko tallafawa "aikin su") wanda nake ganin yana rungumar da yada akidar da take cutar da al'ummarmu.
Yana da free.
Kamar yadda muke", in ji shi.
Kafin wasan kwaikwayon, rapper ya sanar a shafin Twitter cewa ya canza sunansa, yana mai cewa yanzu "a hukumance ana kiransa Kanye West".
Ba shi ne dan wasan farko da ya canza sunansa ba; yana bin sawun Diddy, wanda aka fi sani da Puff Daddy, Puffy da P Diddy.
Rapper Snoop Dogg ya yi suna Snoop Lion kuma ba shakka, sabon tarihin kiɗa, Prince, ya canza sunansa zuwa alama kuma daga baya mai zane-zane wanda aka sani da sunan Prince.
