Tauraruwar Game of Thrones Kit Harington ta kai hari ga maza masu guba
Kit Harington sananne ne saboda rawar da yake takawa a matsayin Jon Snow a cikin HBO's Game of Thrones.
Dan wasan mai shekaru 31 ya kai hari kan yadda ake kallon jarumin da ya ke nuna bambanci tsakanin maza da mata, yana mai cewa irin wadannan rawar da ake takawa a kan allo na nuna cewa matasa a lokuta da dama suna bukatar su zama masu taurin kai domin a girmama su.
Da yake magana da The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya ce "wani abu ya ɓace" kuma ya yi mamakin yadda za a magance matsalar cutarwa ta maza a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri mai wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones, Rose Leslie, mai shekaru 31, ya yarda cewa yana jin "ƙarfi" don magance matsalar.
"Ni kaina, ina jin karfi a yanzu. Me muka yi da namiji?"
"Me muke koya wa maza yayin da suke girma, dangane da matsalar da muke fuskanta yanzu?"
Kit ya yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya zama wani ɓangare na haɓaka masculinity mai guba saboda halayen maza da yawa.
Ya ci gaba, "Mecece haihuwarmu da kuma abin da aka koya mana?
Abin da ake koyarwa a talabijin da kuma a kan titi; abin da ke sa matasa su ji cewa dole ne su kasance wannan bangare na kasancewa namiji?
Ina tsammanin wannan shine babban tambayar zamaninmu: ta yaya zamu canza wannan?
Domin, a fili, wani abu ya ɓace a cikin waɗannan yara".
A cikin hirar, ya kuma yarda cewa ba zai yi wani wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones ba ko kuma na gaba lokacin da jerin suka ƙare a lokacin bazara, yana mai cewa "ya isa da dawakai da fagen fama".
Daga watan Nuwamba, Kit zai fara wasan kwaikwayon Sam Shepard na True West, wanda ke ba da labarin wani mai samar da fina-finai da ɗan'uwansa, wanda ɓarawo ne.
Kwanan nan, ɗan wasan ya bayyana cewa yana jin cewa saduwarsa da matarsa, Rose, ita ce mafi kyawun Game of Thrones.
"Na sadu da matata a wannan shirin, saboda haka, a wata hanya, ta ba ni iyalina na gaba da rayuwata daga yanzu", in ji shi.
