HIV/AIDS: China ta bayar da rahoton karuwar sabbin kamuwa da cutar da kashi 14 cikin 100
Kasar Sin ta sanar da karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV ko AIDS.
Ya shafi mutane sama da 820,000 a kasar, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya.
An samu sabbin mutane 40,000 a cikin kwata na biyu na shekarar 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka sun kasance ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ya nuna canji daga baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV ta yadu cikin sauri a sassan kasar Sin sakamakon kamuwa da jini.
Amma, adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Duk da haka, a shekara-shekara, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV ko AIDS a China ya ƙaru da 100,000.
Cutar da ke saurin yaduwa ta hanyar jima'i na da matukar damuwa a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An yi wa luwadi wariya a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma an ce nuna bambanci ga mutanen LGBT ya yadu.
Domin ra'ayoyin da suka fi na gargajiya a ƙasar, bincike ya nuna cewa tsakanin kashi 70 zuwa 90 na mazajen da suke yin jima'i da maza za su yi aure da mata.
Yawancin yaduwar cutar ta fito ne daga rashin kariya ta jima'i a cikin waɗannan alaƙar.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da hanyoyin magance cutar HIV ga kowa a kasar, a matsayin wani bangare na kokarin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa wani ma'aikaci ya leaked bayanai na Republican jam'iyyar 'yan majalisar dattijai, "dangantaka ƙarya" da kuma "tsarin makirci"
A ranar Asabar, wakilin Amurka Maxine Waters ta yi tir da zargin cewa wani ma'aikacinta ya wallafa bayanan sirri na wasu 'yan majalisar dattijai uku na jam'iyyar Republican a shafukan Wikipedia na 'yan majalisa.
'Yar Democrat ta Los Angeles ta ce ana yin maganganun ne ta shafukan yanar gizo da masu sharhi na "hannun dama".
"Ƙarya, ƙarya, da kuma ƙara ƙaryata", in ji Waters a cikin wata sanarwa a shafin Twitter.
An ce, bayanan da aka fitar sun hada da adireshin sirri da lambobin waya na Sanatocin Amurka Lindsey Graham na South Carolina, da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, dukansu na Utah.
Bayanan sun bayyana a yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis, wanda wani ba a san shi ba ya wallafa a Capitol Hill, hedkwatar gwamnatin Amurka, yayin sauraron kwamitin majalisar dattawa game da zargin rashin dacewar jima'i da ake yi wa dan takarar kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh.
Wannan bayanan ya fito ne jim kadan bayan da 'yan majalisar dattijai uku suka yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya, kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState, sun ba da rahoton cewa adireshin IP ɗin da ke gano asalin sakonnin yana da alaƙa da sashen Waters kuma sun bayyana bayanin wani memba na ma'aikatan Waters, Capitol Hill ya ruwaito.
"Wannan zargi mara tushe karya ne kuma karya ce", Waters ya ci gaba.
"Majalisarmu, wadda aka yi wa karya da kuma yaudara, ba ta da alhakin wannan bayanan da aka fitar.
Wannan tuhuma da ba ta da tushe ba ƙarya ce kuma karya ce kwarai".
Bayanin Waters nan da nan ya haifar da suka kan layi, gami da na tsohon Sakataren Fadar White House Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan ƙaryatawar ta kasance cikin fushi", in ji Fleischer.
"Ya nuna cewa ba shi da halin zama dan majalisa.
Idan aka zargi wani da abin da bai yi ba, kada ka yi fushi.
Kada ka yi ƙoƙari ka yi hakan.
Kada ka yi shakkar dalilin da ya sa mai tuhumar ya yi hakan.
Ya kamata ya kasance mai natsuwa da natsuwa".
Ya bayyana cewa Fleischer yana kwatanta yadda Waters ya yi da sukar da 'yan Democrat suka yi wa Mai Shari'a Kavanaugh, wanda masu sukar suka zargi da yin fushi sosai a lokacin sauraron ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar Republican wanda ya tsaya takarar tsige Waters a zaben tsakiyar shekara, shi ma ya bayyana ra'ayinsa a shafin Twitter.
"Da ma na yi farin ciki da hakan ya faru", in ji ta a shafinta na Twitter.
A cikin sanarwar da ya bayar, Waters ya ce ma'aikatarsa ta gargadi "masu tilasta bin doka da hukumomi masu dacewa game da waɗannan zarge-zargen.
"Za mu tabbatar da gano wadanda suka aikata laifin", ya ci gaba, "da kuma cewa za a dauki alhakin duk wani abin da suka aikata wanda ke da lahani da kuma hadari ga kowa da kowa a cikin tawagar".
Ra'ayi game da Johnny English Strikes Again (Johnny English: Sake Aiki), ɗan fashin leken asiri mara ƙarfi na Rowan Atkinson
An riga an yi al'ada don neman mahimmancin Brexit a cikin sabbin fina-finai daga mahangar Burtaniya kuma da alama wannan na iya amfani da shi ga dawowar wannan fim ɗin Johnny English na parody da comedy, wanda ya fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya dawo da rai a cikin 2011 tare da Johnny English Reborn ( Johnny English Returns).
Shin za a juya wannan abin dariya game da batun wauta da muke da ita a cikin sabon damar fitar da kaya ga al'umma?
Ko ta yaya, ɗan wasan kwaikwayo na Johnny English mai ƙyalli da fuskar roba ya sabunta lasisinsa don ɓata abubuwa a karo na biyu. Sunansa ya riga ya nuna cewa wannan babban abu ne na almara wanda aka tsara don yankunan masu son fim ɗin da ba Turanci ba.
Hakika, shi ne ɗan ɓoye na ɓoye wanda, duk da ƙarancin da'awarsa na ƙarancin ƙarancin ƙarancin ƙarancin ƙarancin ƙarancin Clouseau, ɗan ɗan Mr Bean, da ɗan ɗan ɗan wannan mutumin wanda ya ba da gudummawa guda ɗaya a cikin taken motocin wuta a bikin buɗe gasar Olympics ta London ta 2012.
Hakanan an fara shi ne da ɗan ɗan jakadan duniya mai ban mamaki wanda Atkinson ya taɓa yin sa a cikin tallan TV na Barclaycard da aka manta da shi, wanda ke haifar da hargitsi a hanyarsa.
Akwai wasu lokuta masu kyau a cikin wasan karshe na Johnny English.
Ina son lokacin da Johnny English ya kusanci wani jirgi mai saukar ungulu yana sanye da rigar yaƙi ta zamanin da kuma sawun rotor dinsa suna ta busawa a kan kwalkwali.
Kyautar Atkinson ga wasan kwaikwayo na zahiri yana da kyau, amma yana ba da ra'ayi cewa abin dariya ba shi da ƙarfi kuma ba shi da mahimmanci, musamman lokacin da irin waɗannan fina-finai masu "mai tsanani", kamar 007 da Mission Impossible, sun riga sun yi amfani da wasan kwaikwayo a matsayin ɗaya daga cikin abubuwan da suka dace.
Kamar dai an yi wa yara dariya, maimakon manya, kuma a ganina, baƙon abin da Johnny English ya yi ba shi da basira ko kuma mai da hankali kamar yadda Atkinson ya yi a fim din da ba shi da sauti yayin da yake nuna hali na Bean.
Yanzu dai batun da ya fi kowa sani shi ne cewa Birtaniya na da matsala.
Wani dan fashin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin gidan yanar gizo na leken asiri na Burtaniya kuma ya bayyana asalin duk jami'an Burtaniya a yankin, ga bakin cikin jami'in da ke aiki, wani ɗan ƙaramin rawar da Kevin Eldon ya taka.
Wannan shi ne babban abin da ya faru ga wata firaminista mai girman kai da rikici, wadda ta riga ta sha wahala daga rikicewar rashin amincewa da siyasa: Emma Thompson ta ba da mafi kyawun kanta tare da wannan hali wanda kusan yayi kama da Theresa May, amma ba za a iya yin yawa ba tare da rubutun.
Masu ba da shawara a kan harkokin tsaro sun gaya masa cewa tun da yake dukan 'yan leƙen asiri da ke aiki a yanzu sun yi alkawari, dole ne ya cire wani daga cikin 'yan tawayen.
Kuma wannan yana nufin Johnny English da kansa, wanda yanzu yake aiki a matsayin malami a wata ma'aikata mai ban mamaki, amma yana koyar da darussan ba tare da izini ba game da yadda za a zama ɗan leƙen asiri; a cikin wannan ɓangaren akwai wasu ban dariya, lokacin da Turanci ya ba da makarantar leƙen asiri ga makarantar rock.
An dawo da Turanci zuwa Whitehall don taron gaggawa kuma ya sake saduwa da tsohon abokin aikinsa Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya sake buga shi.
Bough yanzu mutum ne da ya auri kyaftin din jirgin ruwa, rawar da Vicki Pepperdine ke takawa.
Don haka Batman da Robin na Sirrin Sirrin Mai Martaba sun sake shiga cikin aiki, suna haɗuwa da kyakkyawar femme fatale ta Olga Kurylenko, Ophelia Bulletova.
A halin yanzu, Firayim Minista na kasala cikin hatsari ga wani mai karfin hali na fasaha wanda ya ce zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na Birtaniya: Jason Volta mai ban tsoro, wanda Jake Lacy ya buga.
Turanci da Bough sun fara odyssey na wauta na wauta: suna saye da suturar masu shayarwa, suna ƙone gidan cin abinci na Faransa mai ban mamaki; suna haifar da rikici wanda ya sanya su cikin jirgin ruwan Volta na alatu; kuma Turanci ya haifar da cikakken rashin tsari ta hanyar ƙoƙarin amfani da kwalkwali na gaskiya don sanin abin da ke cikin gidan Volta.
Hakika, duk wani abin da aka kama ya fito ne daga wannan fim din, amma abin ban haushi da kuma ban tsoro da ya yi, kamar dai an ɗauko shi ne daga wani shirin talabijin na yara.
Sakamakon ya kasance daidai.
Kuma kamar yadda na yi da sauran fina-finan Johnny English, na kasa daina tunani: Shin masana'antar fim ta Burtaniya ba za ta iya ba Rowan Atkinson rawar da za ta yi daidai da baiwa da take da ita ba?
Jam'iyyar Labour ta musanta cewa tana shirin sa 'yan Birtaniya su yi aiki kwana hudu a mako, amma su biya domin kwana biyar.
Jam'iyyar Labour ta Jeremy Corbyn na duba wani tsari na musamman wanda zai sa 'yan Birtaniya su yi aiki kwana hudu a mako amma su biya na kwana biyar.
A cewarsa, jam'iyyar tana son masu kasuwanci su ba da kuɗin da suka samu ta hanyar juyin juya halin fasaha na wucin gadi (AI) ga ma'aikata ta hanyar ba su karin rana.
A wannan hanyar, ma'aikatan za su ji daɗin hutun mako na kwana uku, amma za su ci gaba da samun albashi iri ɗaya.
Majiyoyi sun ce wannan ra'ayin zai "daidaita" da tsarin tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar da kuma shirin da take na karkatar da kasar ga masu aiki.
Taron Kungiyoyin kwadago ya goyi bayan sauye-sauyen kwana hudu a mako a matsayin wani mataki na yadda ma'aikata za su iya cin gajiyar sauyin tattalin arziki.
Wani babban jami'in jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa The Sunday Times cewa: "Ana sa ran za a sanar da sake duba manufofin kafin karshen shekara.
"Ba zai faru ba dare ɗaya, amma aikin kwana huɗu na aiki burin da ya dace da tsarin jam'iyyar don daidaita tattalin arziki don amfanin ma'aikata, da kuma dabarun masana'antar jam'iyyar gaba ɗaya".
Jam'iyyar Labor ba za ta kasance farkon wanda ya goyi bayan irin wannan ra'ayin ba, kamar yadda Jam'iyyar Green Party ta yi alkawarin mako hudu na aiki a lokacin kamfen dinta na babban zaben 2017.
Duk da haka, a halin yanzu jam'iyyar Labour ba ta goyon bayan burin gaba daya ba.
Wani mai magana da yawun jam'iyyar Labor ya ce, "Aikin kwana hudu ba shi da wata manufa a jam'iyyar kuma ba a yin la'akari da ita".
Shadow Chancellor John McDonnell ya yi amfani da taron jam'iyyar Labour na makon da ya gabata don ya karfafa ra'ayinsa na juyin juya halin zamantakewar al'umma a tattalin arziki.
Mista McDonnell ya ce yana da niyyar dawo da ikon "masu zartarwa da ba a san su ba" da kuma "masu fashin baki" a kamfanonin gwamnati.
Shirin na shadow chancellor kuma yana nufin yiwuwar cewa masu hannun jari na yanzu na kamfanonin ruwa ba za su dawo da duk jarin su ba, saboda gwamnatin Labor na iya yin "yanke-yanke" saboda rashin daidaito da aka gani.
Ya kuma tabbatar da tsare-tsaren sanya ma'aikata a kan kwamitocin kamfanoni da kuma samar da kudaden mallakar kowa don ba da kashi 10 cikin 100 na hannun jari na kamfanoni masu zaman kansu ga ma'aikata, wanda ke ba da gudummawar shekara-shekara har zuwa £ 500.
Lindsey Graham da John Kennedy sun gaya wa "60 Minutes" idan binciken da FBI ta yi game da Kavanaugh zai iya canza ra'ayinsu
Binciken da hukumar ta FBI ke yi game da zargin da ake yi wa mai shari'a Brett Kavanaugh ya jinkirta akalla mako guda a kan zaben da za a yi na zabensa a kotun koli, inda aka yi tambaya ko binciken da hukumar ta samu zai iya janyo hankalin 'yan majalisar dattijai na Republican su janye goyon bayansu.
A wata hira da aka yi da shi a ranar Lahadi, ɗan jaridar "60 Minutes" Scott Pelley ya tambayi 'yan majalisar wakilai John Kennedy da Lindsey Graham, 'yan Republican, ko FBI za ta iya bayyana wani abu da zai sa su canja ra'ayinsu.
Kennedy ya fi takwaransa na South Carolina faɗin gaskiya.
"Ina nufin, ba shakka", in ji Kennedy.
"Na ce zan je wurin. Na yi magana da Alkalin Kavanaugh.
Na kira shi bayan da aka gabatar da karar kuma na tambaye shi ko ya yi hakan.
Ya kasance mai ƙarfi, mai ƙuduri, mai ƙarfi".
Duk da haka, ƙuri'ar Graham kamar ba za a iya canja ta ba.
"Ra'ayina game da Brett Kavanaugh ya tabbata kuma zan yi zargin fashewa", in ji shi.
"Dr. Ford, ban san abin da ya faru ba; amma na san wannan: Brett ya musanta shi sosai", Graham ya kara da cewa, yana nufin Christine Blasey Ford.
"Kuma mutanen da ka ambata ba su iya tabbatar da hakan ba.
Wannan ya faru ne shekaru 36 da suka gabata.
Ba na ganin wani sabon abu".
Menene bikin Global Citizen kuma ya yi wani abu don rage talauci?
A wannan Asabar, birnin New York zai yi bikin Global Citizen Festival, wani biki na shekara-shekara na kiɗa da ke da taurari masu ban sha'awa da kuma manufa mai ban sha'awa, wato kawar da talauci a duniya.
A shekara ta bakwai, bikin Global Citizen zai ga dubban mutane suna ta zagayawa a filin Great Lawn na Central Park, ba wai kawai don jin daɗin wasan kwaikwayon Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin taron na kawar da talauci kafin 2030.
Bikin Global Citizen, wanda aka fara a shekarar 2012, wani bangare ne na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya ce ta tallafi ta kasa da kasa da ke fatan kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da talauci.
Domin samun tikiti kyauta don taron (sai dai idan kuna son biyan tikitin VIP), masu halarta dole ne su kammala jerin ayyuka ko "ayyuka", kamar su ba da gudummawa, aika imel ga shugaban duniya, yin kiran waya, ko kuma duk wata hanya mai ma'ana don taimakawa wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da burin kawar da talauci.
Amma, menene nasarar da Global Citizen ta samu bayan shekaru 12 da cimma burinta?
Shin ra'ayin bayar da kyauta ga mutane da wasa kyauta hanya ce ta gaske ta shawo kan mutane su nemi a dauki mataki ko kuwa wani lamari ne na abin da ake kira "clictivism", mutane suna tunanin cewa suna nuna bambanci ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takarda ta yanar gizo ko aika tweet?
Tun daga 2011, Global Citizen ta ce ta samu fiye da "share" miliyan 19 daga mabiyanta, inda ta samar da wasu manufofi.
Ya ce wadannan ayyuka sun taimaka wajen karfafawa shugabannin duniya gwiwa wajen sanar da kudaden da suka kai fiye da dala biliyan 37 da aka sadaukar domin shafar rayuwar mutane sama da biliyan 2.25 nan da shekarar 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta kawo alkawura 390 da kuma sanarwar da aka samu daga hannun jarin ta, wanda a kalla dala biliyan 10 aka biya ko aka karba.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa, har zuwa yanzu, kudaden da aka tanada sun shafi mutane miliyan 649 a duniya.
Wasu daga cikin muhimman alkawuran sun hada da The Power of Nutrition, wata kungiya ta masu zuba jari da masu gudanarwa a Burtaniya da ta yi alkawarin "taimaka wa yara su bunkasa zuwa ga iyawarsu", tare da alkawarin samar wa Rwanda da dala miliyan 35 don taimakawa wajen kawo karshen rashin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar bayan karbar tweets sama da 4700 daga Global Citizen.
"Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu bayar da tallafi, hukumomin kasa da kuma masu goyon bayan Global Citizen kamar ku, za mu iya mayar da rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a cikin bayanin kula na tarihi", in ji jakadan The Power of Nutrition, Tracey Ullman, a lokacin wani taron kai tsaye a watan Afrilu na 2018 a London.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce bayan an yi ayyuka sama da 5,000 na inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga mata da yara a Burtaniya, gwamnati ta sanar da kudade ga aikin The Power of Nutrition wanda zai kai mata da yara miliyan 5 tare da maganganun abinci mai gina jiki.
A amsa ga wata tambaya da ake yawan yi a shafinsa, "Me ya sa kake ganin za mu iya kawar da talauci?"
Global Citizen ta amsa: "Za mu yi tafiya mai tsawo da wuya, kuma wani lokacin za mu yi kasala.
Amma kamar yadda ya faru da manyan ƙungiyoyin kare hakkin bil'adama da na nuna wariyar launin fata da suka riga suka wuce, za mu yi nasara, domin tare, mu ne mafi ƙarfi.
Janet Jackson, the Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B da Janelle Monae wasu daga cikin masu fasahar da za su yi a taron na wannan shekara a New York, wanda Deborra-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman za su gabatar.
Amurka na iya amfani da ruwan teku don yin "kulle" don hana fitar da makamashin Rasha, Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka ya sanar
"Idan ya zama dole", Washington na iya amfani da teku don hana makamashin Rasha zuwa kasuwannin da suka hada da na Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka, Ryan Zinke, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ta ruwaito.
Zinke ya yi ikirarin cewa, shigar Rasha cikin Syria, musamman inda take aiki a karkashin umarnin gwamnati, wata hujja ce ta gano sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Ina ganin dalilin da ya sa suke Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne domin suna son su yi ciniki da makamashi kamar yadda suka yi a Gabashin Turai", in ji shi, kamar yadda aka ruwaito.
Kuma, a cewar jami'in, suna da hanyoyi da kuma hanyoyin da za su iya magance shi.
"Amurka tana da ikon, tare da rundunar sojin ruwa, na tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin ruwa suna bude, kuma idan ya zama dole, ta toshe su don tabbatar da cewa makamashin ba ya zuwa kasuwa", in ji shi.
Zinke ya yi magana ne ga mahalarta taron da kungiyar Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta da ke kiran kanta "muryar masu amfani da makamashi" a Amurka.
Ya kwatanta dabarun Washington wajen ma'amala da Rasha da Iran, ya yi la'akari da cewa, a aikace, abu ɗaya ne.
"Zaɓin tattalin arziki a Iran da Rasha ya fi ko ƙasa da amfani da maye gurbin man fetur", in ji shi, yayin da yake magana game da Rasha yana cewa "yana da dabara ɗaya kawai" tare da tattalin arziƙin mai.
An yi maganganun ne yayin da gwamnatin Trump ke kan aikin bunkasa fitar da iskar gas dinta zuwa Turai, domin maye gurbin Rasha, wacce ita ce mafi arha ga masu amfani da Turai.
Don haka, jami'an gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da shugaban, sun yi kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta janye daga aikin "ba daidai ba" na aikin Nord Stream 2, wanda Trump ya ce ya mayar da Berlin "bautar" Moscow.
Moscow ta sha jaddada cewa aikin mai na Nord Stream 2 mai dala biliyan 11, wanda aka kafa don ninka karfin mai na yanzu zuwa murabba'in mita biliyan 110, aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
Kremlin ta yi jayayya cewa, tsananin adawa da Washington ke yi da aikin na nuna dalilai na tattalin arziki ne kawai, kuma misali ne na rashin adalci.
"Ina ganin mun yarda cewa wutar lantarki ba za ta iya zama kayan aiki na matsa lamba ba kuma ya kamata masu amfani su sami damar zabar masu samar da su", in ji Ministan makamashin Rasha Aleksandr Novak, bayan ganawa da Sakataren makamashin Amurka Rick Perry, wanda ya gudana a watan Satumba a Moscow.
Matsayin Amurka ya sami martani daga Jamus, wanda ya sake tabbatar da jajircewar sa ga aikin.
Babbar kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, Federation of German Industries (BDI), ta yi kira ga Amurka da ta janye daga manufofin makamashi na EU da yarjejeniyar biyu tsakanin Berlin da Moscow.
"Ina da babbar matsala idan wata kasa ta uku ta tsoma baki a samar da makamashi", in ji Dieter Kempf, shugaban BDI, bayan ganawar da aka yi kwanan nan tsakanin shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel da shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
Elizabeth Warren za ta yi la'akari sosai da takarar shugabancin kasar ta 2020, in ji Sanata daga Massachusetts
A ranar Asabar, Sanata Elizabeth Warren daga Massachusetts ta ce za ta yi nazari sosai kan takarar shugabancin kasar bayan zaben tsakiyar shekara.
A lokacin taron jama'a a Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ya tabbatar da cewa zai yi la'akari da takararsa.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su gyara gwamnatin da ta karye, kuma hakan ya hada da mace a kan mulki", in ji ta, a cewar The Hill.
"Bayan 6 ga Nuwamba, zan yi la'akari sosai da neman shugabancin kasa".
Warren ya yi tsokaci kan shugaba Donald Trump a taron jama'a, yana mai cewa yana "ja da kasar nan zuwa hanyar da ba ta dace ba.
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyarmu", in ji ta.
Warren ya yi magana a fili game da Trump da kuma wanda ya tsaya takararsa a kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh.
A ranar Juma'a, Warren ya yi tsokaci a shafinsa na Twitter cewa, "Tabbas, akwai bukatar bincike daga FBI kafin a kada kuri'a".
Duk da haka, wani zabe da aka fitar a ranar Alhamis ya nuna cewa yawancin masu zaɓe na Warren ba su yi imani cewa zai tsaya takara a shekarar 2020 ba.
Kashi hamsin na masu jefa kuri'a a Massachusetts sun ce ba za ta tsaya takara ba, a cewar wani binciken da Cibiyar Binciken Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk da Boston Globe suka gudanar.
Kashi talatin da biyu cikin dari sun goyi bayan takarar.
Binciken ya nuna goyon baya ga takarar tsohon gwamna Deval Patrick, tare da goyon baya kashi 38 cikin dari ga takarar da za a iya yi da kuma kashi 48 cikin dari a kan hakan.
