Biden ya ce zai yanke shawara a hukumance kafin watan Janairu, in ji kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press.
Sarah Palin ta yi tsokaci game da matsalar tashin hankali ta Post Traumatic Stress Disorder (PTSD) da Track Palin ya yi a taron Donald Trump
Track Palin, mai shekara 26, ya shafe shekara guda a Iraki bayan ya shiga aikin soja a watan Satumba
A ranar Litinin da daddare, an kama shi kuma an tuhume shi da laifin tashin hankali na cikin gida.
"Abin da ɗana yake fuskanta, abin da ke faruwa a yanzu, na ga abin da ke faruwa a wasu iyalai da ke fama da sakamakon PTSD da kuma wasu raunuka da sojojinmu ke kawowa", in ji ta a wani taron Donald Trump a Tulsa, Oklahoma.
