Jihohi 18 da Gundumar Columbia sun kalubalanci sabon tsarin neman mafaka
Jihohi 18 da Gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan daukaka kara kan sabuwar manufar Amurka da ta hana baƙi mafaka daga wadanda ke gudun hijira daga tashin hankali na cikin gida ko kuma kungiyoyin masu aikata laifi.
A ranar Juma'a, wakilan jihohi 18 da na gundumar sun gabatar da wani rahoto na goyon bayan kotu a Washington don tallafawa mai neman mafaka da ke ƙin siyasa, NBC News ta ruwaito.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai shigar da kara a shari'ar Sessions da Grace ba.
Ta ce mijinta "da 'ya'yanta daga wata kungiya mai aikata laifuka" sun yi mata fyade, amma jami'an Amurka sun ki amincewa da neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga watan Yuli.
Sun kama ta a Texas.
Lauyoyin jihohin da ke goyon bayan Grace sun bayyana El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, wadanda ke samar da masu neman mafaka da yawa a Amurka, a matsayin kasashen da ke fuskantar matsalolin da suka shafi kungiyoyin aikata laifuka da kuma tashin hankali na cikin gida.
Sabuwar manufar neman mafaka ta Amurka ta soke shawarar da aka yanke a shekarar 2014 daga Hukumar Daukaka Kararrakin Shige da Fice da ta ba da damar baƙi marasa tushe da ke tserewa daga tashin hankali na cikin gida su nemi mafaka.
Babban lauyan gundumar Columbia Karl Racine ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa a ranar Juma'a cewa sabuwar manufar "ta yi watsi da shekarun da suka gabata na dokokin jihohi, tarayya da na kasa da kasa".
"Dokar tarayya ta bukaci a yanke wa duk wani neman mafaka hukunci bisa ga takamaiman yanayi da kuma gaskiyar da ake nema, kuma wannan haramcin ya sabawa wannan ka'ida", in ji rahoton da ke goyon bayan kotun.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ci gaba da muhawara a cikin rahoton cewa dokar hana shigo da baƙi na cutar da tattalin arzikin Amurka, suna mai cewa za su iya zama 'yan kasuwa kuma su "ba da aiki".
A watan Yuni, babban lauya Jeff Sessions ya umarci alƙalan shige da fice da su daina bai wa wadanda suka tsere daga cin zarafin gida da kuma ta'addancin ƙungiyoyin masu laifi mafaka.
"Ana samun mafaka ga wadanda suka bar kasarsu saboda tsanantawa ko tsoron saboda launin fata, addini, kasa ko kuma kasancewa cikin wani rukuni na zamantakewa ko ra'ayi na siyasa", in ji Sessions a sanarwar manufofinsa na ranar 11 ga Yuni.
Ba a taɓa nufin mafaka ta sauƙaƙa dukan matsaloli (har ma da manyan matsaloli) da mutane suke fuskanta a kowace rana a dukan duniya ba.
A halin yanzu ana ta kokarin ceto a Palu, yayin da adadin wadanda suka rasa rayukansu ke ninkawa, a cikin gagarumar gagarumar neman wadanda suka tsira.
Ga waɗanda suka tsira, yanayin ya ci gaba da taɓarɓarewa.
"Yanayin na da matukar wahala", in ji mahaifiyar mai suna Risa Kusuma, mai shekara 35, tana ta'azantar da jaririnta mai zazzaɓi a cibiyar kwashe mutane daga garin Palu da ke fama da bala'i.
"Kowane minti wani motar asibiti tana zuwa da gawawwakin.
Kuma babu ruwa mai tsafta".
An ga mazauna garin suna komawa gidajensu da suka lalace, suna tattara kayansu da suka nutse, suna kokarin ceton duk wani abu da suka samu.
Akwai daruruwan mutane da suka ji rauni kuma asibitoci, waɗanda girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta lalata, sun cika.
Wasu daga cikin wadanda suka ji rauni, ciki har da Dwi Haris, wanda ya karya kashin baya da kafada, suna kwance a waje da Asibitin Sojojin Palu, inda ake kula da marasa lafiya a waje saboda ci gaba da mummunan girgizar kasa.
Hawaye suka zubo masa idanu yayin da yake bayyana yadda ya ji girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta girgiza dakin otal dinsa na bene na biyar da yake zaune da matarsa da 'yarsa.
"Babu lokacin da za a cece mu.
Ruwan bangon ya murkushe ni, ina tsammanin", in ji Harris ga Associated Press, ya kara da cewa danginsa suna bikin aure a garin.
"Na ji matata tana kuka don taimako, amma sai na yi shiru.
Ban san abin da ya faru da ita ko 'yata ba.
Ina fata kun kasance lafiya".
Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da yin amfani da "tallace-tallacen farfaganda"
Makon daya bayan wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wani sanarwa mai shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka da ke tallata amfanin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana game da shafin biyan kuɗi na China Daily a cikin Des Moines Register, jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa, bayan da ya zargi China da tsoma baki a zaben da za a yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, abin da China ta musanta.
Zargin da Trump ya yi na cewa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka, ya nuna abin da jami'an kasar suka rubuta a Reuters a matsayin wani sabon mataki na kara yakin neman zabe na Washington don tilasta wa China.
Duk da yake al'ada ce gwamnatocin kasashen waje su fitar da tallace-tallace don inganta kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington a halin yanzu suna cikin yakin kasuwanci mai tasowa wanda ke ganin daidaita haraji a kan kayayyakin da suke shigowa da su.
A cewar masana na China da Amurka, an tsara takunkumin kwastam din da China ta yi a farkon yakin cinikayya don cutar da masu fitar da kaya daga jihohi kamar Iowa, wanda ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, daya daga cikin manyan masu fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa kasar Sin, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da 'yan kasuwa.
Wani labarin da Branstad ya rubuta da aka buga a cikin jaridar Moines Register ta ranar Lahadi, ya nuna cewa China "tana kara wannan kamfen na cin zarafi ta hanyar yada tallace-tallace na farfaganda a cikin jaridar Amurka kyauta".
"A cikin yada farfagandarsu, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi amfani da al'adar Amurka mai daraja na 'yancin magana da latsa ta hanyar buga wani talla na biya a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"A akasin haka, a gidan jarida da ke ƙarshen wannan titi a Beijing, akwai 'yan muryoyin masu saɓani kaɗan kuma ba a ga ainihin tunani game da ra'ayoyin da Sin ke da su game da yanayin tattalin arzikin China mai ban tsoro, saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna ƙarƙashin ikon jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin", in ji shi.
Ya kuma ce "ɗaya daga cikin manyan jaridu a China ta ƙi tayin buga" labarinsa, duk da cewa bai tabbatar da jaridar da yake ba.
Kavanaugh ya yi watsi da kuri'un mata 'yan Republican kwanaki kadan kafin zaben rabin shekara
Duk da cewa yawancin manyan 'yan Republican suna goyon baya da kuma kare Brett Kavanaugh, dan takarar babban kotu, duk da zargin da ake yi masa na cin zarafin mata, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa za a yi tashin hankali, musamman daga mata masu jefa kuri'a, a zaben da za a yi a tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa.
An yi tawaye sosai game da zargin, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun tsaya don ci gaba da jefa kuri'a.
"Ba za a iya kawar da waɗannan abubuwa ba", in ji Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin ilimin siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell a Jami'ar Syracuse a wata kasida da aka buga a ranar Lahadi a The Hill.
Reeher ya kuma ce yana da shakkar cewa lokacin karshe na Sanata Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) don binciken FBI zai isa ya kwantar da hankalin masu jefa kuri'a.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba, kuma ba za su manta da shi ba a nan gaba ko a watan Nuwamba", in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara kuma mai magana da yawun ƙungiyar ci gaba ta MoveOn, a cikin jaridar Washington, D.C.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a, masu adawa da "Kusan Nuwamba!" sun yi zanga-zanga a cikin harabar majalisar dattawa, yayin da 'yan Republican, tare da ikon Kwamitin Shari'a, suka yanke shawarar ci gaba da nadin Kavanaugh, duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, in ji Mic.
"Gurgumin da kuma himmar 'yan Democrat za su wuce duk wani zato", in ji Stu Rothenberg, wani mai sharhi kan siyasa.
"Gaskiya ne, ya riga ya yi girma,
amma za a samu ƙarin, musamman ma a tsakanin mata masu jefa kuri'a da ke cikin unguwannin da ke da nisa ko kuma waɗanda suke tsakanin shekara 18 zuwa 29, waɗanda ko da yake ba sa son shugaban ƙasa, ba sa yawan zuwa zaɓe".
Kafin shaidar Ford ta bayyana dalla-dalla zargin cin zarafin da ya yi wa dan takarar na Kotun Koli, manazarta sun ba da shawarar cewa zai iya fuskantar tashin hankali idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da tabbatarwa.
"Wannan ya zama bala'i ga jam'iyyar Republican", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National, a farkon makon nan a NBC News.
"Wannan ya wuce zaben kwamitin, ko zaben karshe ko kuma ko Kavanaugh zai zauna a kan kujerar da ake tuhuma ko a'a. Matsalar ita ce yadda 'yan Republican suka yi da kuma yadda suka bi da ita", in ji Guy Cecil, darektan Priorities USA, kungiyar da ke taimakawa zaben 'yan Democrat a tashar labarai.
Duk da haka, kamar dai jama'ar Amirka sun rarrabu tsakanin ko za su yarda da shaidar Ford ko ta Kavanaugh, ko da yake sun fi karkata ga goyon bayan na biyun.
Wani sabon bincike na YouGov ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin dari na mutanen da aka yi wa tambayoyi sun gaskata da shaidar Ford, ko kuma sun yi imani da ita, idan aka kwatanta da kashi 35 cikin dari na mutanen da suka goyi bayan shaidar Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun yi imanin cewa Kavanaugh zai iya yin ƙarya a lokacin da yake ba da shaida, idan aka kwatanta da kashi 30 cikin ɗari da suka yi imanin cewa Ford zai yi hakan.
Bayan matsin lamba da Flake ya yi, FBI tana binciken tuhumar da Ford ya gabatar, da kuma na akalla wata mai tuhumar, Deborah Ramirez, in ji jaridar The Guardian.
A makon da ya gabata, Ford ta shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata hari a lokacin da ta ke 'yar shekara 17.
A maimakon haka, Ramirez ya yi ikirarin cewa dan takarar kotun koli ya nuna mata al'aura a wani bikin koleji lokacin da take karatu a Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo yana son kirkirar sabuwar intanet domin ya yi gogayya da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya kaddamar da wani kamfanin farawa don yin gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Inrupt, sabon aikin wannan almara na fasaha, kamfani ne da ke kan Solid, Berners-Lee's open source platform.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za su adana bayanan su da kuma waɗanne mutane za su iya samun damar waɗanne bayanai.
A wata hira ta musamman da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi hasashen cewa burin da Inrupt ke da shi shi ne "mulkin duniya".
"Dole ne mu yi hakan", in ji shi game da farawa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu "ma'ajiyar bayanan sirri na kan layi" ko POD.
Za ka iya samun jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin abubuwan da za a yi, kalandarku, kiɗa, da kuma wasu kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify suna samuwa a cikin mai bincike ɗaya a lokaci guda.
Abin da ya sa wannan rumbun adana bayanan sirri na musamman shi ne cewa mai amfani yana da cikakken iko kan wanda zai iya samun damar abin da ke cikin bayanan.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan "karfafa mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar shugabanta John Bruce, ita ce kamfanin ya kawo albarkatu, matakai da ƙwarewar da ta dace don taimakawa wajen sanya Solid a duniya.
Kamfanin yanzu ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, kamfanin tsaro na IBM, wasu masu haɓaka da aka yi wa haya don aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen sa kai.
Farawa daga wannan makon, masu haɓaka daga ko'ina cikin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen su na rarraba tare da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya bayyana cewa shi da tawagarsa ba su yi magana da "Facebook ko Google ba game da ko za su yi wani canji na gaba daya da zai sauya tsarin kasuwancin su cikin dare.
"Ba mu bukatar izininka".
A wata kasida da aka buga a ranar Asabar a cikin Medium, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "umurnin Inrupt shine samar da wutar lantarki da kuma tsarin halittu wanda zai taimaka kare mutunci da ingancin sabon gidan yanar gizo mai tushe na Solid".
A 1994, Berners-Lee ya canza Intanet ta hanyar kafa ƙungiyar World Wide Web Consortium a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya tashi a matsayin mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Har ma a lokacin ƙaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee ya kasance wanda ya kafa kuma ya jagoranci ƙungiyar World Wide Web Consortium, da kuma kungiyoyin yanar gizo na yanar gizo da kuma Open Data Institute.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da wannan sabuwar zamanin yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
Taya ga Bernard Vann, limamin da aka ba da lambar yabo ta Victoria a yakin duniya na farko
Limamin Cocin Ingila guda daya da aka ba da lambar Victoria Cross a lokacin yakin duniya na farko an ba shi girmamawa bayan mutuwarsa a garinsu shekaru 100 bayan haka.
An ba da lambar yabo ga Lieutenant Colonel da Reverend Bernard Vann a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, a cikin harin Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Duk da haka, wani dan bindiga ya kashe shi bayan kwana hudu ba tare da sanin cewa an ba shi babbar lambar yabo ta soja ta Burtaniya ba.
A ranar Asabar, jikokinsa biyu ne suka kaddamar da wani abin tunawa a cikin girmamawa a wani biki a Rushden, Northamptonshire.
Michael Vann, daya daga cikin jikokinsa, ya jaddada alamomin gano wannan abin tunawa shekaru 100 bayan aikin kakansa wanda ya ba shi lakabi.
A cewar London Gazette, a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, Laftanar Colonel Vann ya jagoranci rukuninsa ta Saint-Quentin Canal "ta cikin hazo mai yawa da kuma ƙarƙashin ikon wuta mai ƙarfi na injin-makami".
Daga baya ya hanzarta zuwa layin wuta kuma, tare da "babban ƙarfin hali", ya jagoranci layin gaba kafin ya yi hanzari tare da bindiga kuma ba tare da taimakon kowa ba, kuma ya kashe mutane uku daga cikin abokan gaba.
An kashe Laftanar Kanar Vann da wani dan kunar bakin waken Jamus a ranar 4 ga watan Oktoba, 1918, wata daya kafin yakin ya kare.
Michael Vann, mai shekara 72, ya ce abin da kakarsa ya yi "wani abu ne da ba zai taɓa iya rayuwa da shi ba, amma darasi ne duk da haka".
Shi da ɗan'uwansa Dr. James Vann sun kuma sanya kambi na furanni bayan bikin, wanda ya jagoranci ƙungiyar matasa ta Brentwood Imperial.
Michael Vann ya ce yana jin "girma sosai da ya shiga cikin bikin" kuma ya kara da cewa "jarumtar wannan jarumin ta nuna goyon bayan mutane da yawa".
Peppa Pig ta yanke wa magoya bayan MMA a mafi kyawun lokaci
Ka yi tunanin kana barci dukan dare don ka ji daɗin wasan kwaikwayon Bellator 206, sai ka ga cewa wani abu ya hana ka yin hakan.
