Desert Island Discs: Tom Daley ya ji kasa saboda jima'i
Tom Daley, dan tsalle-tsalle na Olympics, ya ce ya girma yana jin kasa da kowa saboda jima'i, amma wannan ya sa ya sami kwarin gwiwa don cin nasara.
Wannan dan wasa mai shekara 24 ya ce bai fahimci cewa ba kowa ba ne kamarsa har sai da ya isa makarantar sakandare.
Baƙon wasan farko na shirin Desert Island Discs na Radio 4 wanda Lauren Laverne ta jagoranta, ya bayyana cewa ya fara magana game da haƙƙin ɗan luwadi don ba da bege ga wasu.
Ya kuma raba cewa kasancewa uba ya taimaka masa wajen daidaita mahimmancin cin gasar Olympics.
Kirsty Young, wadda take gabatar da wannan shirin, tana kan hutun rashin lafiya.
A matsayin bako a shirin farko da Laverne ta jagoranta, Daley ya raba cewa yana jin "kasa" da sauran mutane saboda "ba a yarda da shi ba cewa kuna son yara maza da mata".
Ya ce: "Har wa yau, wannan ra'ayin kasa da bambancin da nake da shi ne ya sa na ci gaba da samun nasara".
Yana son ya nuna cewa shi wani ne don kada mutane su ji kunya sa'ad da suka gano cewa shi ɗan luwaɗi ne.
Tare da lambobin tagulla biyu na wasannin Olympics, ya zama fitaccen mai fafutukar LGBT kuma ya yi amfani da bayyanarsa a wasannin Commonwealth na Australiya don yin kira ga ƙarin ƙasashe don yanke hukunci game da luwadi.
Ya yanke shawarar yin magana ne domin yana jin ya yi sa'a ya rayu a fili ba tare da tsoron wata sanarwa ba, kuma yana son ya ba da bege ga wasu.
Gwarzon dan wasan duniya sau uku ya ce yin soyayya da mai shirya fim din Amurka Dustin Lance Black, wanda ya sadu da shi a shekarar 2013, "abin mamaki ne".
Daley ta auri wannan dan wasan Oscar a shekarar da ta gabata kuma ta ce bambancin shekaru 20 da suka gabata bai taba zama matsala ba.
"Idan ka rayu tsawon wannan lokaci a cikin gajeren lokaci" (yana da shekaru 14 kawai ya fara shiga gasar Olympics kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon daji shekaru uku bayan haka), yana da wuya a sami wani a shekarunka da ya sami irin wannan tashin hankali.
Ma'auratan sun haifi ɗansu na farko a watan Yuni, Robert Ray Black-Daley, kuma wannan haihuwar ta sa Daley ya canza ra'ayinsa gaba ɗaya.
"Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, babban abin da ya motsa ni shi ne na lashe lambar zinare", in ji shi.
"Amma yanzu na san cewa akwai abubuwa da suka fi lambar zinare ta Olympics muhimmanci.
A gare ni, Robbie ne lambar yabo ta".
An sa wa ɗansa suna bayan mahaifinsa Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana da shekaru 40 saboda ciwon daji na kwakwalwa.
