Tana da ƙwararrun masana goma da suka horar da su, waɗanda suke yin bincike a kai a kai, suna bincika yara, kuma a wasu lokatai suna yin ceto.
Har ila yau, kungiyar tana da wurin ajiye bat na farko a Scotland a Threave Estate a Dumfries da Galloway, wanda ke da gida ga nau'in bat takwas daga cikin goma na Scotland.
David Thompson, manajan gidaje, ya ce wannan shi ne wuri mafi kyau da za su iya zama.
