Ma'aikatar lafiya ta aika wasika ga ma'aikatan EU a NHS na Scotland inda ta nuna godiyarta ga Scotland da kuma fatan ta na su zauna a Scotland bayan Brexit.
Jeane Freeman MSP ta aika da wasika kasa da watanni shida kafin Birtaniya ta fice daga EU.
