Jack Ross: "Na karshe burina shi ne na iya horar da Scotland".
Manajan Sunderland, Jack Ross, ya bayyana cewa "buƙatarsa ta ƙarshe" ita ce ta zama kocin Scotland a wani lokaci.
Dan wasan Scotland mai shekara 42 yana jin daɗin kalubalen farfado da kungiyar daga arewa maso yamma, wacce a halin yanzu take matsayi na uku a League One, maki uku daga kansa.
Ya zo filin wasa na Stadium of Light a wannan bazarar bayan ya jagoranci St Mirren zuwa gasar farko ta Scotland a kakar wasa ta bara.
"Lokacin da nake dan wasa, burina shi ne in buga wa kasarmu wasa.
Na buga wasa sau daya a tawagar B, kuma wannan shine komai", in ji Ross a shirin BBC Scotland na Sportsound.
"Na girma ina kallon Scotland tana wasa a Hampden sau da yawa tare da mahaifina lokacin da nake yaro, wani abu da nake son sake rayuwa.
Amma wannan dama za ta zo ne idan na yi nasara a matsayin shugaban kulob".
A baya dai Ross ya jagoranci Sunderland a matsayin kocin kungiyar, inda ya hada da Dick Advocaat, David Moyes, Sam Allardyce, Martin O'Neill, Roy Keane, Gus Poyet da kuma Paulo Di Canio.
Tsohon manajan Alloa Athletic ya ce bai ji damuwar da za ta haifar da irin wadannan mutane masu karfi a babban kulob din ba bayan da ya ki amincewa da shawarwarin da Barnsley da Ipswich Town suka gabatar masa.
"Sakamakon da zan samu a wannan lokacin zai dogara ne a kan ko zan iya mayar da wannan kulob din cikin gasar Premier?
Domin tsarin da wuraren da kungiyar ke ciki babu shakka na kulob din Premier ne", in ji shi.
"Ba zai zama aiki mai sauƙi ba in zo, amma zan iya ganin cewa na yi nasara a nan idan zan iya mayar da kulob din zuwa Premier".
Ross ya yi shekara uku ne a matsayin kocin bayan ya yi aiki a matsayin mataimakin kocin Dumbarton da kuma wata 15 a matsayin kocin Hearts.
A wannan lokacin ya taimaka wa Alloa ta dawo daga koma baya zuwa rukuni na uku kuma ya sami St Mirren daga kusan koma baya don lashe gasar Championship a kakar wasa ta gaba.
Ross ya ce ya fi jin dadi yanzu fiye da yadda ya taɓa ji yayin wasan Clyde, Hartlepool, Falkirk, St Mirren da Hamilton Academical.
"Wataƙila na kasance a kan hanyar da ta dace", in ji shi, game da kula da Alloa.
"Na yi tunani cewa horarwa ta fi kyau a gare ni, fiye da wasa.
Wannan ya zama abin mamaki domin ban yi kasala ba, na samu kuɗi mai yawa kuma na yi nasara.
Amma wasa zai iya zama da wuya.
Akwai abubuwa da yawa da za ku shawo kansu kowane mako.
Har ila ina fama da damuwa da matsin lamba na aiki, amma ina jin daɗin motsa jiki.
A koyaushe ina jin daɗin motsa jiki, kuma yanzu da nake yin hakan, ina jin na fi jin daɗi fiye da dā a rayuwata ta balaga".
