Eilidh Doyle za ta zama "muryar 'yan wasa" a kwamitin hukumar wasannin motsa jiki ta Scotland
An zabi Eilidh Doyle a kan kwamitin kungiyar wasannin motsa jiki ta Scotland a matsayin darakta mai ba da izini a babban taron shekara-shekara na kwamitin gudanarwa.
Doyle ita ce 'yar wasan Scotland da aka fi ba da lambar yabo, kuma shugaban Ian Beattie ya bayyana wannan matakin a matsayin babbar dama ga waɗanda ke jagorantar wasan don cin gajiyar kwarewar ta a duniya a cikin shekaru goma da suka gabata.
"Eilidh na da mutunci sosai a cikin al'ummar Scotland, a Burtaniya da kuma duniya, kuma muna da tabbacin cewa wasannin motsa jiki na Scotland za su amfana sosai daga shigarsa cikin kwamitin", in ji Beattie.
Doyle ya bayyana haka: "Ina matukar son zama mai magana da yawun 'yan wasa kuma ina fatan zan iya ba da gudummawa da taimakawa wajen jagorantar wasanni a Scotland".
'Yar Amurka, wacce ta lashe mita 200 da mita 400 a wasannin Atlanta na 1996 tsakanin jimillar 'yan wasan zinare na Olympics kuma a halin yanzu tana aiki a matsayin mai ba da labari na yau da kullun ga BBC, ta sha wahala daga wani ciwon ischemic na ɗan lokaci wanda ya hana ta iya tafiya.
