Wata girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da kuma tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, bisa ga majiyoyin hukuma, sun yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane akalla 384, kuma ana sa ran adadin zai ci gaba da karuwa.
Saboda katsewar sadarwa, ba a samu wani bayani daga yankin Donggala ba, yankin da ke arewacin Palu wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5.
A Palu, sama da mutane 16,000 ne aka kwashe bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Celebes:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Celebes ta Tsakiya, wanda ke a ƙarshen kunkuntar bakin teku a gabar yamma ta tsibirin Celebes, tare da kusan mutane 379,800 a cikin shekarar 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekara 40 da haihuwar sa sa'ad da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku.
Donggala yanki ne wanda yake kan iyakar tekun kilomita 300 a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Celebes.
Wannan yankin, yanki ne na yanki wanda bai kai lardin ba, yana da mazaunan kusan 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Kamun kifi da noma sune manyan ginshikan tattalin arzikin lardin Celebes ta Tsakiya, musamman a yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Ma'adinan nickel ma suna da mahimmanci a lardin, amma galibi suna da hankali a Morowali, a gefen tekun Célebes.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata bisa ga Hukumar Rage Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya kuma afkawa yammacin Donggala a shekarar 1996, inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana kan yankin Pacific Ring of Fire da ke da yawan girgizar kasa, saboda haka tana fuskantar girgizar kasa a kai a kai.
Waɗannan su ne wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka faru a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra, wanda ya faru a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi kasashe 14, wanda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Wani jerin girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa gabar yammacin Sumatra a karshen watan Maris da farkon watan Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane suka mutu a tsibirin Nias, a gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudancin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami da ya lalata gabar tekun kudu, inda ya yi sanadiyyar mutuwar mutane kusan 700.
2009: An yi girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.6 a kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Yammacin Sumatra.
Fiye da mutane 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai da ke gabashin Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 da ya hallaka ƙauyuka da dama kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa mai saurin kaiwa a yankin Pidie Jaya dake Aceh, ya haifar da bala'i da fargaba, yayin da mutane ke tuna da mummunan bala'in da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka yi a shekarar 2004.
A wannan lokacin ba a sami wata annobar tsunami ba, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu saboda gine-gine da suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afku a tsibirin Lombok na Indonesiya, inda ta yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane sama da 500, mafi yawansu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar kasa ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido a cikin wani yanayi na wucin gadi.
An kama babban dan Sarah Palin bisa zargin cin zarafin cikin gida
An kama Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa Sarah Palin, bisa zargin kai hari.
An kama Palin, mai shekaru 29, dan asalin Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin aikata laifukan tashin hankali na cikin gida, hana gabatar da rahoton tashin hankali na cikin gida da kuma adawa da hukuma, a cewar wata sanarwa da jami'an tsaron jihar Alaska suka fitar.
Rahoton 'yan sanda ya ce, sa'ad da wata abokinta ta yi ƙoƙarin kiran 'yan sanda don su kai ƙarar, sai 'yan sanda suka kwace wayarta.
Palin na tsare a gidan yari a Mat-Su Pretrial Facility tare da belin dala 500, kamar yadda KTUU ta ruwaito.
Ya bayyana a gaban kotu a ranar Asabar, inda ya bayyana cewa "ba shi da laifi, a bayyane yake" lokacin da aka tambaye shi, kamar yadda gidan yarin ya ruwaito.
Palin tana fuskantar laifuffuka guda uku na Class A, wanda ke nufin za ta iya shiga kurkuku har shekara guda kuma za a iya tara ta da dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin laifi na B, wanda ake iya hukuntawa da ranar ɗaurin kurkuku da kuma tarar dala dubu biyu.
Wannan ba shi ne karo na farko da aka kai ƙarar Palin ba.
A watan Disamba na 2017, an zarge shi da kai wa mahaifinsa hari, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarta, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don su kai rahoton harin.
Yanzu haka dai shari'ar tana gaban kotun tsoffin sojoji na Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an zarge shi da cin zarafin cikin gida, hana gabatar da rahoton tashin hankali na cikin gida da kuma mallakar makamai a cikin maye dangane da lamarin.
Budurwarsa ta zarge shi da ba shi kyauta a fuska.
An soki Sarah Palin daga kungiyoyin tsoffin sojoji a cikin 2016 bayan ta danganta halayyar ɗanta mai tashin hankali da cutar ta PTSD da take fama da ita bayan ta yi aiki da sojojin a Iraki.
Girgizar kasa da tsunami a Indonesia sun kashe daruruwan mutane
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu bayan girgizar kasa da ta afkawa tsibirin Celebes na Indonesia ranar Juma'a.
Girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya lalata dubban gidaje.
Wutar lantarki da hanyoyin sadarwa ba su da isasshen, kuma ana sa ran adadin mutanen da suka mutu zai ƙaru a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
Girgizar kasa ta afku ne a gaban Celebes Central, a arewa maso gabashin Jakarta babban birnin kasar Indonesia.
Bidiyon da ke nuna lokacin da aka yi ambaliyar ya bazu a shafukan sada zumunta.
Daruruwan mutane ne suka taru a wani biki a bakin rairayin bakin teku a garin Palu lokacin da tsunami ya afkawa gabar teku.
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya na neman a yi wa wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a birnin New York hukuncin kisa.
Masu gabatar da kara na New York suna kokarin yanke hukuncin kisa kan Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci da ya kashe mutane takwas a birnin New York, hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa a jihar ba tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi zargin cewa ya yi amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar keke a kan titin West Side Highway na Lower Manhattan, yana kashe masu tafiya da ƙafa da masu hawan keke da ya gamu da su a cikin watan Oktoba.
Don a ba da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe wadanda aka kashe "da gangan" kuma ya yi musu mummunan rauni "da gangan", a cewar sanarwar da aka gabatar a yankin kudancin New York.
Dukkanin laifuffukan biyu suna da damar da za a iya yanke musu hukuncin kisa bisa ga takardar kotu.
Makonni bayan harin, wata kotun tarayya ta gurfanar da Saipov kan laifuka 22, ciki har da laifuka takwas na kisan kai tare da hadin gwiwar kungiyar aikata laifuka, wanda ake amfani da shi a lokuta da dama a cikin shari'ar masu gabatar da kara, da kuma laifukan tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci "shirye-shirye da kuma tunani sosai", in ji masu gabatar da kara yayin da suke bayyana yadda Saipov ya kai harin da ya yi kama da "m, mai zalunci da lalata".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco rauni, lalacewa da kuma asarar dukiya" kamar yadda aka bayyana a cikin sanarwar niyyar tuhuma.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
An yi shekaru goma da aka daina yin shari'ar kisa a gundumar New York ta Kudu.
An yanke wa Khalid Barnes hukuncin kisa kan masu safarar miyagun kwayoyi biyu, amma daga karshe an yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
Lokaci na ƙarshe da aka yi amfani da hukuncin kisa a cikin shari'ar tarayya ta New York shine a cikin 1953, a cikin shari'ar Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa don yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe Rosenbergs a kan kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, wanda aka haifa a Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin nadama a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin bisa ga takardun kotu.
Ya shaida wa masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗi game da abin da ya yi, kamar yadda 'yan sanda suka ce.
Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa, don kai harin, ya yi amfani da bidiyon ISIS da ya duba a wayarsa bisa ga tuhumar.
Ya kuma nemi a ba shi damar ganin tutar ISIS a dakin asibitinsa, 'yan sanda sun ce.
Ya ce bai yi laifi ba a kan laifukan da aka tuhume shi da su 22 ba.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce sun "yi matukar takaici" da hukuncin da aka yanke.
"Mun yi imanin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar hukuncin daurin rai da rai ba tare da yiwuwar sakewa ba zai kara tsawaita raunin da wadannan abubuwan suka haifar ga duk wadanda abin ya shafa", in ji Patton.
Kungiyar kare Saipov ta riga ta nemi masu gabatar da kara da kada su nemi hukuncin kisa.
Wani dan majalisa mai ra'ayin Tory ya ce ya kamata a sanya NIGEL FARAGE a matsayin shugaban tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin "karfafa rundunar mutane" a yau a lokacin zanga-zangar taron Tory.
Tsohon shugaban jam'iyyar Independence Party na Burtaniya ya ce dole ne 'yan siyasa su "ji matsin lamba" daga masu shakkar Turai (lokacin da daya daga cikin 'yan majalisar Theresa May ya ba da shawarar cewa ya kamata ya dauki bakuncin tattaunawar da EU.
Dan majalisa Peter Bone ya bayyana a gaban taron Birmingham cewa da Birtaniya ta riga ta fice daga EU da Mr Farage ne sakataren Brexit.
Amma kalubalen da Mrs May ke fuskanta na sulhunta bangarorin jam'iyyarta da ke da saɓani ya bayyana a fili lokacin da Tories masu goyon bayan tsayawa a EU suka shiga cikin wani zanga-zangar 'yancin kai da aka gudanar a birnin.
Firayim Minista na fafutukar kiyaye alkawuran da ta dauka na shirin Chequers a tsakanin hare-haren masu goyon bayan Brexit, masu adawa da EU.
Abokan kawancensa sun nace masa ya ci gaba da gwagwarmaya don kokarin cimma yarjejeniya da Brussels duk da cewa an amsa shi da baki, don tilasta wa masu shakkar Turai da kuma Labour su zabi tsakanin shirinsa da rudani.
Mista Bone ya bayyana a taron kungiyar Leave Means Leave na Solihull cewa yana son ya kawo karshen shirin Chequers.
Ya ba da shawarar cewa ya kamata a yi amfani da Mr Farage don ɗaukar nauyin tattaunawar tare da Brussels.
"Da a ce an ba shi mukami, da mun riga mun fita daga EU a yanzu", in ji shi.
Dan majalisar Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: "Zan ci gaba da goyon bayan Brexit, amma dole ne mu soke shirin Chequers".
Da yake nuna adawarsa ga EU, ya bayyana haka: "Ba mu yi yaƙe-yaƙe na duniya don a yi mana hidima ba.
Muna son mu kafa dokokinmu a ƙasarmu.
Mista Bone ya musanta wasu shawarwari da ke nuna cewa ra'ayin jama'a ya sauya tun bayan zaben 2016: "Hankalin da ake da shi cewa mutanen Burtaniya sun sauya ra'ayinsu kuma suna son su ci gaba da kasancewa cikin EU ba gaskiya ba ne".
'Yar majalisa ta Tory kuma mai goyon bayan Brexit Andrea Jenkyns ta halarci wannan gangamin, inda ta yi wa manema labarai jawabi: "Abin da nake cewa shi ne: Firayim Minista, ka saurari jama'a.
"Shirin Chequers ba shi da kyau a cikin jama'a, 'yan adawa ba za su amince da shi ba, ba su da kyau a cikin jam'iyyarmu da kuma masu fafutuka waɗanda, da farko, su ne waɗanda ke zaune a kan tituna kuma suna ba mu damar zaɓa.
Ka soke shirin Chequers kuma ka fara sauraronsa.
A cikin wata sako ga Mrs May, ya kara da cewa: "Firaministoci suna kiyaye aikinsu idan sun cika alkawuransu".
Mista Farage ya ce a taron dole ne a "ji wa 'yan siyasa haushi" idan suna da niyyar cin amanar shawarar da aka yanke a zaben raba gardama na 2016.
"Yanzu wannan batun amincewa ne tsakanin mu, jama'a, da kuma siyasa", in ji shi.
"Suna kokarin cin amanar shawarar Brexit kuma mun taru a nan yau don gaya musu cewa ba za mu bari su yi nasara ba".
A cikin wata sako da ya aika wa jama'a, ya kara da cewa: "Ina so ku sanya 'yan siyasarmu, wadanda ke gab da cin amanar shawarar Brexit, su ji ba su da dadi.
"Muna tattara sojojin mutanen wannan kasa da suka ba mu nasara a kan Brexit kuma ba za su huta ba har sai mun zama Burtaniya mai alfahari, mai zaman kanta da kuma mai cin gashin kanta".
A halin yanzu, masu goyon bayan Remain sun yi tafiya ta Birmingham kafin su gudanar da taron sa'o'i biyu a tsakiyar gari.
Wasu 'yan gwagwarmaya sun yi ta yada banners da ke dauke da sakon Tories Against Brexit bayan kaddamar da kungiyar a karshen mako.
Dan jam'iyyar Labour, Lord Adonis ya yi wa 'yan Conservatives ba'a kan matsalar tsaro da suka fuskanta a wata manhajar jam'iyyar a farkon taron.
"Waɗannan mutane ne ke gaya mana cewa za su iya samun tsarin IT da kyau da kuma duk fasahar da ta fi dacewa ga Kanada, don samun iyakar da ba ta da matsala, don jin daɗin kasuwa kyauta ba tare da iyaka a Ireland ba", in ji shi.
Wannan ba gaskiya ba ne.
Ya kara da cewa, "Babu wata ma'anar Brexit mai kyau".
Warren yana shirin yin tunani sosai game da tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta yi tunani sosai game da neman takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben na watan Nuwamba.
Jaridar Boston Globe ta ruwaito cewa 'yar Democrat daga Massachusetts ta yi magana game da makomarta a ranar Asabar yayin taron gari a wani gari a yammacin Massachusetts.
Warren, mai sukar shugaban kasa Donald Trump, zai sake tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa a watan Nuwamba a kan 'yan Republican Geoff Diehl, wanda ya yi mata takarar shugabancin Trump a shekarar 2016 a Massachusetts.
Tana cikin abubuwan da ake hasashen za ta gaji Trump a 2020.
Taron na yammacin Asabar a Holyoke shi ne taro na 36 da ya yi da masu jefa kuri'a ta amfani da tsarin majalisa tun lokacin da Trump ya zama shugaban kasa.
Wani mataimakinsa ya tambaye shi ko yana shirin tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa.
Warren ya amsa cewa lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su gyara matsalolin gwamnatinmu, kuma don haka ne muke bukatar mace a matsayin shugaban kasa.
An kama wani mutum dangane da harin da ya kashe Sims, dan wasan LSU
