Wayde Sims ya ji rauni a kan kansa kuma ya mutu sakamakon hakan, in ji shugaban 'yan sanda Murphy J. Paul a cikin sanarwar da ya bayar ga kafofin watsa labarai a ranar Asabar ta hanyar 247sports.
Wayde ya shiga don kare abokinsa kuma Simpson ya harbe shi.
An yi wa Simpson tambayoyi kuma ya yarda da cewa yana wurin da yake da makami kuma ya yarda da cewa ya harbe Wayde Sims.
An kama Simpson ba tare da wani abu ba kuma an tsare shi a ofishin 'yan sanda na East Baton Rouge Parish.
Sims, dan wasan mai tsayi biyu da ya girma a Baton Rouge, ya buga wasanni 32 tare da farawa 10 a kakar wasa ta bara kuma ya kai kimanin minti 17.4, 5.6 da 2.9 a kowane wasa.
Gasar cin kofin Rasha: Lewis Hamilton ya kusanci lashe gasar cin kofin duniya, saboda yadda tawagarsa ta ba shi damar cin kofin gasar a kan Sebastian Vettel
Ya bayyana sarai tun lokacin da Valtteri Bottas ya sauka a gaban Lewis Hamilton a ranar Asabar cewa umarnin Mercedes zai zama mai mahimmanci a cikin tseren.
Bottas, wanda ya fara daga kan gaba, ya yi kyakkyawan farawa kuma ya kusan barin Hamilton shi kaɗai yayin da yake kare matsayinsa a cikin zagaye na farko da biyu kuma yana gayyatar Vettel don ya kai wa abokin aikinsa hari.
Vettel ya fara shiga cikin akwatin kuma ya bar Hamilton ya yi gudu tare da zirga-zirga a ƙarshen rukuni, wanda zai zama mai yanke hukunci.
Mercedes ta tsaya a cikin boxes bayan daurin daya kuma ya fita a baya Vettel, amma Hamilton ya gaba daya bayan da dama dabaran-da-dabaran manoeuvres cewa sa da Ferrari direba da gangan ya bar free ciki a hadarin da za a rasa baya bayan biyu karewa a karo na uku.
Max Verstappen ya tashi daga jere na ƙarshe na grid na farawa kuma ya hau zuwa wuri na bakwai a ƙarshen zagaye na farko a ranar haihuwarsa ta 21.
Sannan ya jagoranci tseren tsawon lokaci saboda ya kiyaye tayoyinsa don samun saurin zuwa ƙarshen kuma ya wuce Kimi Raikkonen a matsayi na huɗu.
Daga karshe ya shiga fage a zagaye na 44 amma bai iya samun damar shiga matsayi ba a cikin zagaye na takwas na ƙarshe, wanda ya ƙare tare da Raikkonen a matsayi na huɗu.
Rana ce mai wuya, domin Valtteri ya yi aiki mai kyau a duk karshen mako kuma ya kasance mai gaskiya.
Hamilton ya ce, "Kungiyar ta yi aiki mai ban mamaki wajen samun wurare biyu na farko a gasar.
Harshe mara kyau na jiki
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi wa Sanata Dianne Feinstein ba'a a wani taron da aka gudanar a ranar Asabar saboda nacewarta kan cewa ba ta fitar da wasikar Christine Blasey Ford ba inda ta zargi Brett Kavanaugh, dan takarar kotun koli, da cin zarafin mata.
A wani jawabi da ya yi a wani taron da aka yi a West Virginia, shugaban bai yi magana kai tsaye game da shaidar da Ford ya bayar a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa ba, kuma ya yi sharhi a maimakon haka cewa abin da ke faruwa a majalisar dattawa ya nuna cewa mutane sun kasance 'masu wulakanci, masu banƙyama da masu ƙarya'.
"Abin da ya iya faruwa kuma mafi kyau shi ne abin da ke faruwa a kwanakin nan a majalisar dattawa, lokacin da ka ga fushin, lokacin da ka ga cewa mutane suna fushi kuma abin takaici ne, abin ƙyama ne kuma maƙaryaci ne", in ji shi.
Idan ka ga wadannan sakonni da kuma bayanan da suka fito, sai su ce, "Oh, ban yi ba.
Ban kasance ba".
Kuna tuna da shi?
Dianne Feinstein, ka taɓa yin wani abu da ya shafi 'yan jarida?
Ka tuna da amsarsa, ka fitar da takardar? "Oh, oh, me?
Oh, ba haka ba.
Ban kasance ba.
Jira a lokacin.
"Shin mun tace shi?...A'a", ya kara da cewa yana kwaikwayon sanata.
An aika wa Feinstein wasikar da ke bayyana zargin da Ford ya yi wa Kavanaugh a watan Yuli kuma aka leken asirin a farkon watan Satumba, amma Feinstein ya musanta cewa leken asirin ya fito ne daga ofishinsa.
"Ban ɓoye zargin da Dr. Ford ya yi ba, ban kuma ɓoye labarinta ba", in ji Feinstein ga kwamitin kamar yadda jaridar The Hill ta ruwaito.
Ya ce in kiyaye asirinsa, kuma na yi abin da ya ce.
Amma ƙin yarda da shi bai yi wa shugaban kasa dadi ba, wanda ya yi wannan tsokaci a lokacin taron na ranar Asabar da daddare: Ka gaya mana cewa harshen jikinsa bai dace ba.
Wataƙila ba a tace shi ba, amma ya yi amfani da harshen jiki mafi muni da na taɓa gani a rayuwata.
A ci gaba da kare dan takarar kotun koli, wanda wasu mata uku suka zargi da aikata laifuka na lalata, shugaban ya nuna cewa 'yan Democrat suna amfani da zargin ne don amfanin kansu.
Sun ƙudura niyyar dawo da mulki ta kowace hanya.
"Suna da mugunta da banƙyama, ba su damu da wanda suke cutarwa ba, wanda dole ne su ci gaba da yin nasara don dawo da iko da iko", in ji shugaban, a cewar Mediaite.
Elite League: Dundee Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallaye biyu a raga a Dundee
Dundee Stars sun gyara rashin nasarar da suka sha a ranar Juma'a a gasar Elite League da Belfast Giants inda suka ci wasan a Dundee a ranar Asabar da ci 5-3.
Giants sun sami nasara da wuri ta hanyar Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun daidaita zuwa rukunin gida kafin Dwyer ya sake kafa Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya ci Dundee a raga kafin kwallo biyu da Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya ci su suka sa suka ci Dundee.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na uku da 'yan Adam Keefe suka sha kaye a gasar Elite League a kakar bana, inda suka yi nasarar tashi da Dundee da ci 2-1 a Belfast ranar Juma'a da daddare.
