Jagoran 'yan tsiraru a majalisar wakilai, Nancy Pelosi, ta kira dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh "mai tashin hankali" kuma ta ce bai dace da yanayinsa ba don shiga kotun koli.
Pelosi ta yi wadannan kalamai ne a wata hira da ta yi a ranar Asabar a bikin Texas Tribune a Austin, Texas.
"Na kasa daina tunanin cewa idan mace ta taba yin irin wannan hali, zan kira ta da hauka", Pelosi ta bayyana game da yadda ta mayar da martani ga kavanaugh a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa a ranar Alhamis.
Kavanaugh ya musanta zargin cin zarafin Dr. Christine Blasey Ford lokacin da suke matasa.
A lokacin jawabin farko, Kavanaugh ya nuna matukar farin ciki, a wasu lokuta kusan yana ihu da yin magana yayin da yake bayanin danginsa da shekarun makarantar sakandare.
Ya kuma yi Allah wadai da 'yan Democrat a kwamitin, yana mai cewa zargin da ake masa "kisan kai ne da aka tsara" da 'yan adawa suka shirya saboda rashin nasarar Hillary Clinton a zaben shugaban kasa na 2016.
