Ta yaya yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China zai iya zama mai kyau ga Beijing
An yi ta kai hare-hare a farkon yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, kuma duk da cewa yakin bai kare ba, nesa tsakanin kasashen na iya zama mai amfani ga Beijing a cikin dogon lokaci, masana sun ce.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya fitar da gargadi na farko a farkon wannan shekarar yana yiwa manyan kayayyakin kasar Sin haraji, ciki har da bangarorin hasken rana, karfe da aluminum.
Mafi girman tashin hankali ya faru ne a wannan makon tare da aiwatar da sabbin haraji wadanda suka shafi kwatankwacin dala biliyan 200, tare da sanyawa rabin kayayyakin da ke shigowa Amurka daga China.
A duk lokutan da aka kai hari, Beijing ta mayar da martani, a kwanan nan ta kara haraji daga kashi biyar zuwa kashi goma a kan dala biliyan 60 na kayayyakin Amurka.
Kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin yin koyi da matakan Amurka, kuma da kyar tattalin arzikin duniya na biyu ya tsaya cak a nan gaba.
Don a sa Washington ta yi kasala, dole ne a yi biyayya ga bukatunsu, amma yin biyayya ga Amurka a fili zai zama abin kunya ga Xi Jinping, shugaban kasar Sin.
Duk da haka, masana sun ce idan Beijing ta san yadda za ta yi wasa da katunta daidai, matsin lamba na yakin cinikayya da Amurka na iya amfanar China a cikin dogon lokaci ta hanyar rage dogaro da tattalin arzikin biyu.
"Gaskiyar cewa wani saurin yanke shawara a siyasa a Washington ko Beijing na iya haifar da yanayin da ake buƙata don fara rikicin tattalin arziki a ƙasashen biyu ya fi haɗari fiye da yadda aka yarda a baya", in ji Abigail Grace, mai bincike kan Asiya a Cibiyar Sabon Tsaron Amurka, wani cibiyar bincike.
Syria ta shirya don 'yan gudun hijirar su koma, in ji ministan harkokin wajen kasar
Syria ta ce a shirye take da 'yan gudun hijirar su koma gida da son rai, kuma tana neman taimako wajen sake gina kasar da ta girgiza bayan yaki da ya shafe sama da shekaru bakwai.
A jawabinsa ga Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan harkokin wajen kasar Walid al-Moualem ya bayyana cewa yanayin kasar na inganta.
"Yau halin da ake ciki a kan kasa ya fi kwanciyar hankali da tsaro saboda ci gaban da aka samu a yaki da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da gyara wuraren da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata domin dawo da al'amuran al'ada.
Yanzu duk yanayin da ake bukata ya kasance domin dawowar 'yan gudun hijira da son rai zuwa kasar da suka bar saboda ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki na gefe daya da suka shafi rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum da kuma rayuwarsu.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa fiye da 'yan Syria miliyan 5.5 ne suka tsere daga kasar tun lokacin da yakin ya fara a shekarar 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida suna ci gaba da zama a kasar kuma suna bukatar taimakon jin kai.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta yi godiya ga duk wani taimako da za ta iya samu wajen sake gina kasar da ta lalace.
Amma ya ce ba zai amince da taimakon da aka ba shi ba, ko da daga ƙasashen da suka goyi bayan tawayen.
Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Paris
Kungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup ta 2018 ta doke tawagar Amurka da ci 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a kulob din Le Golf National da ke wajen birnin Paris, Faransa.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na shida da Amurka ta ci nasara a Turai, kuma ba ta lashe kofin Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake samun kambin ne lokacin da tawagar kyaftin din Denmark Thomas Bjorn ta kai maki 14.5 da ake bukata domin doke Amurka.
Tauraron Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya fi bayar da nasara a gasar, ya jefa kwallon cikin ruwa a rami na 16 na par 3, ya rasa wasan da Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan Italiya ya yi fice a duk wasannin da ya buga, ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasa hudu da suka ci 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
Jordan Spieth na Amurka ya ci 5 da 4 daga dan wasan da ya fi kowacce a gasar Turai, Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark.
Dustin Johnson na farko a duniya ya rasa 2 da 1 a kan Ian Poulter na Ingila, wanda zai iya buga gasar Ryder Cup ta ƙarshe.
Tsohon ɗan wasan Ryder Cup takwas, ɗan Spain Sergio García ya zama ɗan wasan Turai mafi nasara a gasar, tare da maki 25.5.
"Ba na yawan yin kuka, amma a yau, ba zan iya daina yin kuka ba.
Shekara ce mai wuya.
Ina godiya ga Thomas da ya zaɓe ni kuma ya gaskata da ni.
Ina farin ciki, ina farin ciki da na dawo da kofin.
Abu mafi muhimmanci shi ne tawagar, kuma ina farin cikin cewa na iya taimakawa", in ji wani mai farin ciki Garcia bayan nasarar Turai.
Ya ba da shaidar ga ɗan ƙasarsa John Ram, wanda ya ci Tiger Woods na Amurka 2 da 1 a wasan mutum-mutumin ranar Lahadi.
Rahm, mai shekara 23 ya ce: "Ina alfahari da yadda na yi nasara a kan Tiger Woods. Na girma ne ina kallon wannan yaron yana wasa.
Woods ya rasa wasansa hudu a Faransa kuma yanzu yana da rikodin 13-21-3 a gasar Ryder Cup.
Wannan wani adadi ne mai ban mamaki ga daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasan kwallo na dukan lokaci, wanda ya lashe gasar majors 14 a duniya, wanda ya fi Jack Nicklaus.
Kungiyar Amurka ta yi wahala a duk karshen mako don kada ta fita daga tituna, ban da Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau, waɗanda suka yi wasan golf mai ƙarfi a duk faɗin gasar.
Kyaftin din Amurka Jim Furyk ya bayyana bayan rashin nasarar da tawagarsa ta samu, "Ina alfahari da wadannan yara, sun yi gwagwarmaya.
A safiyar yau, sun sa 'yan Turai cikin matsala na ɗan lokaci.
Mun yi yaƙi.
Na cire hat dina a gaban Thomas.
Kai kyawawan kyaftin ne.
'Yan wasan su 12 sun yi wasa mai kyau.
Za mu sake tsara kanmu, kuma mu yi aiki tare da PGA of America da kuma kwamitin gasar Ryder Cup, kuma za mu ci gaba.
Ina son waɗannan yara 12 kuma ina alfahari da zama kyaftin.
Don cire hat.
Sun fi su".
Bayanan Red Tide: An samu raguwar yawan ruwa a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
A cewar rahoton da aka fitar kwanan nan na Hukumar Kula da Kifin Kifi da Dabbobin Florida, akwai raguwar yawan ruwan sama a sassan yankin Tampa Bay.
A cewar kwamitin, ana ganin yanayin fitowar ruwa a wurare masu tasowa a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da kuma a cikin Counties Collier, wanda hakan na iya nufin cewa ana rage yawan.
Red tide yana kaiwa kusan kilomita 210 na gabar teku daga gundumar Pinellas ta arewa zuwa Lee ta kudu.
Za a iya samun tarin abubuwa mil goma daga gabar tekun gundumar Hillsborough, amma a wurare da yawa idan aka kwatanta da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma gano jan ruwa a gundumar Pasco.
An samu rahoton cewa akwai matsakaitan matakan da ke kan ko wajen gabar ruwan Pinellas County a makon da ya gabata, matattarar ruwa da kuma manyan ruwa a gabar ruwan Hillsborough County, matattarar ruwa da manyan ruwa a ko wajen gabar ruwan Sarasota County, matattarar ruwa da matsakaitan ruwa a Charlotte County, matattarar ruwa da manyan ruwa a ko wajen gabar ruwan Lee County, da kuma ƙananan ruwa a cikin Colier County.
An samu rahotanni cewa a cikin Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da kuma Collier County, ana ci gaba da samun cututtukan rashin jin daɗi na numfashi.
Babu wani irin wannan lamarin da aka ruwaito a arewa maso yammacin Florida a makon da ya gabata.
